        {
            "title": "美國通膨數據走弱後 交易員強化了對聯儲會到年中將會降息的預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"564\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vVEblxHyf9OiaNNq3GPHlQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ff3fa7d40aa7fa0a2214d4720a2d1bb6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在美國通膨數據弱於預期後，債券交易員強化了對於<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>到今年年中將會降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利率互換顯示，交易員認為聯儲會在本月稍晚的政策會議上不會降息，但已完全消化了到6月份將會降息的情景。美債在周二數據公佈後最初走強，但隨著投資者把目光轉向當日稍晚的30年期國債標售，漲勢未能持續。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國12月核心CPI升幅低於預期 通膨下行信號進一步明確 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">品浩(PIMCO)經濟學家Tiffany Wilding在彭博電視上表示，通膨數據「呈現的圖景信號參雜」，「聯儲會必須甄別其中信息」。她表示，在過去三次會議合計降息75個基點之後，聯儲會官員「十分樂於暫停腳步」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dddf2fa6-588d-3951-ae30-6f9b83575c0f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"564\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jqtiNjYSCBDFrAzMLsXQEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4c7c2704e9c4a463d4cdeb8d5d693693\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對貨幣政策最敏感的短期國債在報告公佈後短暫反彈，兩年和五年期殖利率一度下行約3個基點。截至紐約時間上午9:05，兩年期和五年期殖利率當日幾乎持平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道明證券策略師Jan Nevruzi表示：「這無疑會讓市場受到鼓舞。我不認為這會改變對1月的判斷，因為最新的勞動力市場數據已經確定屆時不會有行動。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Traders’ Bets on Fed Cut by June Reinforced by Softer Inflation</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael MacKenzie、Carter Johnson、Alice Gledhill、Kristine Aquino.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%B5%B0%E5%BC%B1%E5%BE%8C-%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E4%BA%86%E5%B0%8D%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E5%88%B0%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-143718321.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 23:27:18",
