        {
            "title": "滙豐前主席杜嘉祺將繼續擔任該行顧問 駐留時間超出原計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"滙豐前主席杜嘉祺將繼續擔任該行顧問 駐留時間超出原計畫\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1BJC.o.kWjwteP0yW3_PzQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/e5f15ae0-f082-11f0-97ae-685dacbaad9c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">滙豐前主席杜嘉祺將繼續擔任該行顧問 駐留時間超出原計畫</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%9D%9C%E5%98%89%E7%A5%BA%E5%B0%87%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E6%93%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%A9%B2%E8%A1%8C%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E9%A7%90%E7%95%99%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E8%B6%85%E5%87%BA%E5%8E%9F%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-112410652.html",
